title: Ww Kielbasa-Bean Slow Cooker Soup
directions: Mix all ingredients, except tomatoes, in a 5 to 6-quart slow cooker (crockpot). Cover and cook on low-heat setting at least 6 hours or until vegetables are tender.
Stir in tomatoes; cover and cook on high-heat setting until heated through, about 15 minutes more. Yields about 1 heaping cup per serving.
ingredients: 58 ounces fat-free chicken broth, four 14 . 5 oz cans
15 ounces canned pinto beans, rinsed and drained
15 ounces canned black beans, rinsed and drained
